release.name: release_2.4.1
release.body:
New features:
* Night shift settings
* Do Not Disturb in shortcuts gallery (#83)
* Invert Scroll Direction (Ventura) in shortcuts gallery
* Evolution can be shown in dual column list (#86)
* Support to customise Evolution icon

Improvement:
* Filter out pre-release from version history
* Evolution document in README
* Tip about keyboard locked in screen test
